The Company has zero liquid Discharge Plant and have fully function Effluent Treatment Plant as under:
1. Stripper System for removing solvent from water;
2. Multiple Effect Evaporator System;
3. Mechanical Vapour Recompression system;
4. Agitated thin Film Dryer;
5. We have fully function RO System;

There is no Zero liquid discharge plant at W-41 & W-42
